habitat_description: This species has been recently described from a spring locality at the margin of the Jollyville Plateau in the city of Austin, Travis County, Texas (Chippindale et al. 2000). Other populations occur in the Jollyville Plateau and Brushy Creek areas of Williamson and Travis counties (Chippindale et al. 2000; Davis et al. 2001; Green et al. 2013). This species would be found in spring outflows, but due to recent landscape changes in the region, assessment of actual status and habitat use are unknown (Davis et al. 2001; Lannoo 2005).
